  <!-- Appendix A2: Continuation in full -->
  <Slide id="appendix-continuation" variant="accent">
    <div class="content-slide appendix">
      <p class="overline overline--appendix">Appendix &middot; A2</p>
      <h2>Continuation &mdash; Every Mechanism</h2>
      <p class="lead appendix__lead">How OmO keeps agents working across stops, restarts, and context walls.</p>

      <div class="appendix__grid">
        <div class="appendix__main">
          <div class="appendix-group">
            <h3 class="appendix-group__title"><span class="appendix-group__num">1</span> &ldquo;Until done&rdquo; loops</h3>
            <ul class="appendix-group__list">
              <li><strong>Ralph Loop</strong> <span class="appendix-group__sep">&middot;</span> agent runs continuously until <code>&lt;promise&gt;DONE&lt;/promise&gt;</code>; auto-resumes if it stops early. Default max 100 iterations.</li>
              <li><strong>ULW Loop</strong> <span class="appendix-group__sep">&middot;</span> Ralph variant with <code>ultrawork</code> mode active &mdash; aggressive parallel execution.</li>
              <li><strong>/start-work</strong> <span class="appendix-group__sep">&middot;</span> Atlas resumes execution from a Prometheus-generated plan in <code>.omo/plans/</code>.</li>
              <li><strong>todo-continuation-enforcer</strong> <span class="appendix-group__sep">&middot;</span> &ldquo;yanks idle agents back to work&rdquo; when todos remain.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="appendix-group">
            <h3 class="appendix-group__title"><span class="appendix-group__num">2</span> State persistence</h3>
            <ul class="appendix-group__list">
